
Before getting started, let's get our system and applications ready.

In order to run ubuntu on cubieboard A20 following things are needed:

1)	Ubuntu 12.04 (Desktop system),

2)	Android SDK (adt-bundle-linux-x86),

3)	SD Card Reader,

4)	Sd card (8 gb),

5)	connectbot app on cubieboard,

6)	android vnc and

7)	lan cable with internet connection on cubieboard
